<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="he-pron">he <strong><em>pron</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /hi:/    美 /hi:/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>他：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>— Where is your brother? 
你兄弟在哪儿？</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>— He's gone to the cinema.
他去看电影了。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.<strong>(指代雄性动物) 它：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Don't be afraid of the dog. He never bites.
别怕这只狗，它从不咬人。</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.<strong>(不论性别的) 一个人；任何人：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He who hesitates is lost.
机会稍纵即逝 / 当断不断，必受其患。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Everybody did what he could.
每个人都尽了力。</p></div></div>